{"version": 2, "width": 100, "height": 30, "timestamp": 1778789057, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "HELIX review: fresh-eyes audit against the governing artifacts"}
[0.0, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m# Build cycle finished. Tests pass. Before merging, a different agent does a fresh-eyes review against the same artifacts that govern the work.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.0, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m> Use HELIX review on the recent OAuth work in this project. Fresh eyes on plan, artifacts, and implementation. Report findings ordered by severity with concrete evidence.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.0, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Skill(skill='helix', args='review the recent OAuth work \u2014 fresh eyes on plan, artifacts, and implementation')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.5, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 Launching skill: helix\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.8, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Bash(command='find docs src tests -type f', description='Enumerate review surface')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.3, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 docs/helix/02-design/security-architecture.md\r\nsrc/auth/refresh.ts\r\ntests/auth/refresh_test.ts\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.6, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='.ddx/beads.jsonl')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.1, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 bead-OAUTH-03 in_review \u00b7 governing \u00a73.2 + \u00a74 \u00b7 evidence: refresh.ts, refresh_test.ts\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.4, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/02-design/security-architecture.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.9, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 30 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.2, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='src/auth/refresh.ts')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.7, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 46 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.0, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='tests/auth/refresh_test.ts')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.5, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 40 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
