[9.154, "o", "\r\n  CRITICAL  \u00a74 revocation list never consulted\r\n            refresh.ts:17-31 validates consumed + expiresAt, then mints.\r\n            evidence: security-architecture.md:18-20 (\"MUST consult\")\r\n\r\n  HIGH      Raw refresh token logged on error path\r\n            refresh.ts:42 \u2014 console.error(`token=${opaqueRefresh}`, err)\r\n            evidence: bead acceptance (\"MUST NOT appear in logs\")\r\n\r\n  HIGH      No test exercises revocation rejection\r\n            refresh_test.ts:37-38 is a TODO comment, not a test.\r\n\r\n  MEDIUM    \u00a74 access-token unwind unimplemented, no recorded scope-out\r\n  MEDIUM    \u00a75 audit row never emitted on any decision path\r\n  MEDIUM    refresh() signature cannot carry \u00a75 audit context (no ctx/IP)\r\n\r\n  LOW       Non-atomic rotation: markConsumed before storeRefresh\r\n  LOW       Bead transitioned to in_review with builder-authored BUG comments\r\n"]
